Wednesday, June 18, 1997

MERIT DOCKET

97-644. State ex rel. Strong v. Killbuck Valley Mosquito Abatement Sanitary Dist.

Wayne App. No. 96CA0054. On amended motion to dismiss. Amended motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.
